    "_scoring_notes": "SCORING INSTRUCTIONS Reverse-score the following items:Extraversion: 6, 21, 31Agreeableness: 2, 12, 27, 37Conscientiousness: 8, 18, 23, 43Neuroticism: 9, 24, 34Openness: 35, 41Next, create scale scores for each domain by averaging the following items (where R indicates using the reverse-scored item).Extraversion: 1, 6R 11, 16, 21R, 26, 31R, 36Agreeableness: 2R, 7, 12R, 17, 22, 27R, 32, 37RConscientiousness: 3, 8R, 13, 18R, 23R, 28, 33, 38, 43RNeuroticism: 4, 9R, 14, 19, 24R, 29, 34R, 39Openness: 5, 10, 15, 20, 25, 30, 35R, 40, 41R, 44Optional items:Liking: 45, 46",
